OL,3,CFans swarm onto pitch as Celtic win
OL,4,CScottish Premiership final
OL,6,FThe Scottish Premiership final turned
OL,7,Finto chaos on Saturday as hundreds of
OL,8,FCeltic fans flooded onto the pitch as
OL,9,Fthe team beat Hearts 3-1 at home.
OL,11,FTheir third goal, cementing their win
OL,12,Fagainst Heart of Midlothian in the
OL,13,F98th minute, brought masses of Celtic
OL,14,Fsupporters onto the turf before the
OL,15,Ffinal whistle had been blown, with
OL,16,Fmany of them seen grabbing players.
OL,18,FHearts striker and captain Lawrence
OL,19,FShankland had to be surrounded by
OL,20,Fstewards and his teammates as some
OL,21,Fsupporters targeted him.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/5
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
