FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1779041473
OL,3,CFans swarm onto pitch as Celtic win
OL,4,CScottish Premiership final
OL,6,FThe side's manager Derek McInnes was
OL,7,Fwalked down the tunnel by police.
OL,9,F"This is bedlam. I don't know if the
OL,10,Ffinal whistle has gone. I can
OL,11,Funderstand the excitement, but this is
OL,12,Fridiculous," Former Celtic striker
OL,13,FChris Sutton could be heard saying on
OL,14,FSky Sports.
OL,16,FIt is the fifth time in a row the
OL,17,FGlasgow side have won the title.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/5
