FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1779041473
OL,3,CFans swarm onto pitch as Celtic win
OL,4,CScottish Premiership final
OL,6,FHearts had taken the lead in the first
OL,7,Fhalf, with Shankland securing a goal
OL,8,Fin the 43rd minute, heightening hopes
OL,9,Fthat the Edinburgh club could secure
OL,10,Ftheir first title since 1960.
OL,12,FBut the hosts equalised in first-half
OL,13,Fstoppage time when Kieran Tierney's
OL,14,Fcross from the left struck the hand of
OL,15,FAlexandros Kyziridis, and Arne Engels
OL,16,Fstepped up to slot the penalty beyond
OL,17,FAlexander Schwolow, who dived the
OL,18,Fright way.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/5
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
