OL,3,CFans swarm onto pitch as Celtic win
OL,4,CScottish Premiership final
OL,6,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FAs tension grew in the second half,
OL,12,FCeltic threatened twice in quick
OL,13,Fsuccession when Kelechi Iheanacho
OL,14,Fstruck a post in the 79th minute,
OL,15,Fbefore Benjamin Nygren's effort was
OL,16,Ftipped over by Schwolow.
OL,18,FThey eventually ground down the long-
OL,19,Ftime leaders when Daizen Maeda turned
OL,20,Fhome substitute Callum Osmand's cross
OL,21,Ffrom close range in the 88th minute.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/5
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
