OL,3,CFans swarm onto pitch as Celtic win
OL,4,CScottish Premiership final
OL,6,FAs Hearts threw numbers forward,
OL,7,Fincluding goalkeeper Schwolow, Osmand
OL,8,Fthen ran clear to knock the ball into
OL,9,Fan empty net, making the score 3-1 in
OL,10,Fthe 98th minute.
OL,12,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,13,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,14,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,15,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,16,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,17,Fbelow...
